_sText:
My first map, all feedback is appreciated. 

A short speedrun map with lots of vertical gameplay. Made for both auto and scroll.

-Easy-medium difficulty. 1m to 2m minute on auto.


It's pronounced "poe-low-gose"
-------------------
CHANGELOG:

-fixed a bunch of skips found by matmo

-fixed triggers floating above blocks and extending past blocks

-improved fps performance (hopefully?)
